<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am so tired of hearing people who DON'T KNOW HOW TO USE THE EBS calling it a train puller. This sword is great. It does more dam per sec than the SSoM, and that calculation is just off of the dam/dly ratio. The Ensnaring Roots is BONUS damage and roots the monster too. For us real gamers out there, who like to actually THINK and STRATEGIZE and utilize our weapons, spells, etc for maximum return, this sword beats the SSoM (the most common alternative to the EBS at certain levels) hands down. If a party says they don't want you because you're using them, screw em. You'll definitely find a party that appreciates this weapon, especially if you know how to use it.</font></td></tr></table>
