<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Novic Goldentip</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-07 16:47:26</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I bought my EBS a while back and so far its been a wonderful weapon.  I use it in my off-hand with an icy blade in my primary hand (if anyone thinks I should switch the placement of these two weaps comments would be greatly appreciated).  The weap hasnt caused any trains so far, however, before going into battle I let my group know and if anyone has any problems with it I switch to my SSoM.  My dex is 124 (w/o buffs) and the weap procs nicely for approx mid 30s dmg(albeit less than the icy blade).<BR>
<BR>
Novic Goldentip<BR>
30th season ranger<BR>
cazic thule server</font></td></tr></table>
