<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Jeroboam</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-10 19:07:11</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>You shouldn't try to use these inside.  Some people on here say "you just need to change your style and some people aren't willing to do it"  Well there is a darn good reason people don't do it.  The reason being it can easily get you killed.  What happens when the mob starts to run and snare is resisted?  Those weapons aren't worth dying or even having to zone.  They don't do THAT much more damage.  When you have to whole fight to get snare to stick you are going to get it.  But when you have 10 seconds before it gets a couple of it's friends on you then you are risking everybody's lives.  So if you walk around underground weilding these don't go whining on the ranger board saying "Rangers suck, people never invite me into a group"  The chances are that you'll kill the group more than you'll help it with a little extra DD.  These are great weapons but keep back up ones that you can use for ALL situations.</font></td></tr></table>
